name: the internet is full of secrets and that is why i <3 2 surf
description: the internet is full of secrets and that is why i <3 2 surf. Made in 2011, when the internet was just starting to coalesce on social media website, the "old web" felt like it was full of hidden secrets of un-tainted self-expression for expression's sake. In 2021, it's starting to make a comeback...
